ds_scraper_cmd is a function
ds_scraper_cmd ()
{
    local cfg=$1;
    case $cfg in
        CQScraper)
            echo "$(which CQScraper.py)"
        ;;
        CQCatchup)
            echo "$(which CQCatchup.sh)"
        ;;
        *)
            echo "$(which scr.py) -s $cfg "
        ;;
    esac
}
